            </p>
          </section>

          {/* Section 4 */}
          <section className="py-8" data-xray-id="pi-section-4">
            <h2 className="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">From Philosophy to Platform</h2>
            <ul className="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
              <li><strong className="text-foreground">Cost+20%</strong>: Every transaction funds the commons — not a corporation, not a government, but the infrastructure you use.</li>
              <li><strong className="text-foreground">Marks</strong>: Effort creates value. You can&apos;t buy your way in. You participate your way in.</li>
              <li><strong className="text-foreground">10-Person Cap</strong>: You matter to exactly 10 people, and they matter to you. That&apos;s a neighborhood, not a corporation.</li>
