              <li><strong className="text-foreground">Beauty</strong> → Hexel design language, craft over commodity</li>
              <li><strong className="text-foreground">Liberty</strong> → Portable reputation, no lock-in, you own your data</li>
              <li><strong className="text-foreground">Equality</strong> → Equal membership ($5/year), Marks earned not bought</li>
              <li><strong className="text-foreground">Justice</strong> → Democratic governance, Areopagus council, transparent rules</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          {/* Section 6 */}
          <section className="py-8" data-xray-id="pi-section-6">
            <h2 className="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Join the Conversation</h2>
            <p className="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-6">
